data.description: Cute rancher - centrally located!  This 5-bedroom home has room for everyone!  The open floor plan on the main level features natural light, master & 2 bedrooms, updated bath and living room.  The spacious kitchen offers adjoining dining space, ample cabinetry and brick-facade backsplash!  Retreat downstairs to the relaxing family room.  This level boasts 2 additional bedrooms and full bath, laundry and storage.  Exit the attached garage to the large, fenced backyard with covered patio, shed and numerous trees!
